node.text: During #TheHills, Brody Jenner shared his reaction to ex Kaitlynn Carter's pregnancy news and the rest was...pretty awkward. Link in bio for their candid convo. (📷: Getty)

node.text: The writer of Crazy, Stupid Love revealed that one of our favorite scenes was completely improvised, and now we love it even more. Trust, the link in our bio is the perfect combination of sexy and cute. (📷: Shutterstock)
